Dialogue: 5,0:02:54.55,0:02:57.48,OP-CH5,,0,0,0,,With the blood and emotions that lived in this heart
Dialogue: 5,0:02:57.88,0:03:00.24,OP-CH5,,0,0,0,,我不会放弃挣扎
